-----Original Message-----
From: Kenneth Phillips [mailto:kphillips@dogbitelaw.com]

Subject: Notice to thePlanet.com re orch8.net

Services, Inc.

Please act upon this notice as required by law.

Sincerely,

Kenneth Phillips

-- 
NOTE: Because I cannot retain e-mail from the public, it is essential

review our prior messages and respond again.

+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

Kenneth M. Phillips, Attorney at Law
